conflating arwen with glorfindel i can understand for the purposes of shortening the film.<br>
putting in extra stuff i don't really see the point (ie, the elves in helms deep, bringing frodo to osgiliath etc).  why was it necessary for frodo to tell sam to feck away off home?<br>
However, i still think they captured the essence of the book and the essence of the major the characters in it.<br>
<br>
as for christopher tolkien, the guy really bores me.  i struggled through most of his commentaries, just to get to the good stuff which his father actually wrote.<br>
